data.description: Beautiful location end of culdesac, NO HOA, bordered by tree farm and farm land. Newly remodeled with lots of space. Exterior new roof, pressure washed, stained decks and shed, most windows have new glass, new complete HVAC, new kitchen, appliances, vanities, toilets, lighting, carpet, vinyl, laminate, paint,  electric wall mount fireplaces, all plumbing, valves, well tank and filter, new well pump, door hardware, mirrors and more. This beautiful home is move in ready- nice views in every direction, 2 family rooms and mud room great for home offices, two decks, paved driveway, 2 car garage finished with heater and attached workshop. Scenic views all around, property borders orchard farm in the rear and tree farm on the side. All measurements approximate and to be verified by buyer.
